Class BasicManager<managedClass>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.JRecord.Common.BasicManager<managedClass>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicNamedManager

    public class BasicManager<managedClass>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores / returns managed classes to the calling program based on a supplied index. i.e. it is a repository for variations on a class.
    Version:
    0.55
    Author:
    Bruce Martin
